<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA58">
<l>mālē paṭiccōti māṟṟē liṉiyuṉatu</l>
<l>pālēpōl cīril paḻuttoḻintēṉ mēlāl</l>
<l>piṟappiṉmai peṟṟaṭikkīḻk kuṟṟēva laṉṟu</l>
<l>maṟappiṉmai yāṉvēṇṭu māṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Māl, don’t change the effulgence of [your] body. Now I</l>
<l>settled in ripening in your milk-like excellence. It is not</l>
<l>furtheron obtaining the absence of birth [and] doing service under [your] foot,</l>
<l>I want, [but] the good of absence of forgetting.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
